items.description: The Gunn World Language Dept will offer its placement tests Thursday August 11th at 10:00 am in G-5, the World Language lab. The test will be proctored by Krissy Ludemann the World Language secretary. Although we will accommodate walk-ins, we would prefer that students sign up in advance. Please email Krissy Ludemann to sign up at kludemann@pausd.org
Please bring your own lunch (no lunch is provided)
